.I papersize
enables the paper format to be set on the command line with the
.RB \[lq] \-d
.BI \%paper= fmt\c
\[rq]
option to
.IR @g@troff .
.
Valid
.IR fmt s
are the ISO and DIN formats
.RB \[lq] A0 \[en] A6 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] B0 \[en] B6 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] C0 \[en] C6 \[rq],
and
