If it is not used with
.IR gropdf ,
the given
.I file
must be a PDF;
.B \%PDFPIC
then relies on the external program
.MR pdftops 1
to convert the PDF to an encapsulated PostScript (EPS) file
and calls the
.B PSPIC
macro with which it shares an interface.
