.ig
For example,
the following macro ignores its arguments,
so calling it is a harmless
(if somewhat busy)
null operation.
..
.
.RS
.IP
.EX
\&.de c
\&..
\&.c This is my comment.
.EE
.RE
.
.
.IP \(bu
Comment lengthy macro definitions.
.
.
.IP \(bu
Use empty requests,
and indentation after control characters,
to clarify a macro's structure.
.
